    <h1>Cache</h1>
    <p class="description">A temporary storage layer that serves saved copies of pages, files, and data instead of regenerating them. Properly configured caching can cut page load times by <strong>50-90%</strong> and directly lifts Core Web Vitals.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
